  <div class="footer-content">
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h3>About the project</h3>
      <p>PACE in the Classroom is an educational resource about the PACE satellite mission and the study of Earth's ecology.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-section">
      <h3>Ссылки</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Main</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About the PACE satellite</a></li>
        <li><a href="/map">Interactive map</a></li>
        <li><a href="/education">Educational materials</a></li>
        <li><a href="/contact">Contacts</a></li>
